  <summary date="2021-08-27T14:03:35Z" status="Introduced in House">Coronavirus Health Care Worker Wellness Act of 2020

This bill requires the Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality to establish a grant program for health care providers to promote mental wellness among frontline health care workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. The agency must also study mental health and burnout among health care workers.</summary>
